#Pi can be operated from your linux machine, its just as easy as using terminal in linux
#It works with a wifi to wifi connection only

1. connect your Pi to the same wifi network as your laptop (home or public network)

2. access terminal in your Pi and enter "ifconfig"

3. you will see the ip address of your pi through which is connected to the network

4. open terminal on your linux machine and execute "ssh pi@x.x.x.x"

5. replace "x.x.x.x" with the ip address you got from ifconfig command 

#enjoy!
